e the first batch,” she said. Vanguard News Nigeria The Management of the University of Benin (UNIBEN) has directed the compulsory use of face masks by staff and students seeking medical attention at the institution’s health centre. Dr. Benedicta Ehanire, Public Relations Officer of UNIBEN, announced the directive in a statement made available to journalists on Tuesday in Benin.… April 21, 2020 In "News" The Management of the University of Benin (UNIBEN), Edo has directed compulsory use of face masks in its campus to curtail the spread of Coronavirus (COVID-19) in the state. April 24, 2020 In "News" The Management of the University of Benin (UNIBEN), Edo has directed compulsory use of face masks on its campus to curtail the spread of Coronavirus (COVID-19) in the state. Dr Benedicta Ehanire, Public Relations Officer of UNIBEN, announced the directive in a statement issued on Friday in Benin. “This is… April 24, 2020 In "Coronavirus Updates"